{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"78c–4","heading":"Security-based swap execution facilities","label":"78c–4 Security-based swap execution facilities","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/ch2B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThis chapter, referred to in subsec. (d)(9)(A)(ii), (10), (14)(B)(v), (C)(i)(I), was in the original “this title”. See References in Text note set out under .section 78a of this title","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective DateSection effective on the later of 360 days after , or, to the extent a provision of subtitle B (§§ 761–774) of title VII of requires a rulemaking, not less than 60 days after publication of the final rule or regulation implementing such provision of subtitle B, see , set out as an Effective Date of 2010 Amendment note under .July 21, 2010Pub. L. 111–203section 774 of Pub. L. 111–203section 77b of this title"],"amendments":["Effective DateSection effective on the later of 360 days after , or, to the extent a provision of subtitle B (§§ 761–774) of title VII of requires a rulemaking, not less than 60 days after publication of the final rule or regulation implementing such provision of subtitle B, see , set out as an Effective Date of 2010 Amendment note under .July 21, 2010Pub. L. 111–203section 774 of Pub. L. 111–203section 77b of this title"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Registration","label":"a Registration","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"No person may operate a facility for the trading or processing of security-based swaps, unless the facility is registered as a security-based swap execution facility or as a national securities exchange under this section.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Dual registration","label":"2 Dual registration","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Any person that is registered as a security-based swap execution facility under this section shall register with the Commission regardless of whether the person also is registered with the Commodity Futures Trading Commission as a swap execution facility.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Trading and trade processing","label":"b Trading and trade processing","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"make available for trading any security-based swap; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"facilitate trade processing of any security-based swap.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Identification of facility used to trade security-based swaps by national securities exchanges","label":"c Identification of facility used to trade security-based swaps by national securities exchanges","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A national securities exchange shall, to the extent that the exchange also operates a security-based swap execution facility and uses the same electronic trade execution system for listing and executing trades of security-based swaps on or through the exchange and the facility, identify whether electronic trading of such security-based swaps is taking place on or through the national securities exchange or the security-based swap execution facility.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Core principles for security-based swap execution facilities","label":"d Core principles for security-based swap execution facilities","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Compliance with core principles","label":"1 Compliance with core principles","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/1/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F1%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the core principles described in this subsection; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/1/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F1%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any requirement that the Commission may impose by rule or regulation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Reasonable discretion of security-based swap execution facility","label":"B Reasonable discretion of security-based swap execution facility","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Unless otherwise determined by the Commission, by rule or regulation, a security-based swap execution facility described in subparagraph (A) shall have reasonable discretion in establishing the manner in which it complies with the core principles described in this subsection.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Compliance with rules","label":"2 Compliance with rules","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F2%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the terms and conditions of the security-based swaps traded or processed on or through the facility; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F2%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any limitation on access to the facility;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F2%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to provide market participants with impartial access to the market; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F2%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to capture information that may be used in establishing whether rule violations have occurred; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"establish rules governing the operation of the facility, including rules specifying trading procedures to be used in entering and executing orders traded or posted on the facility, including block trades.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Security-based swaps not readily susceptible to manipulation","label":"3 Security-based swaps not readily susceptible to manipulation","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The security-based swap execution facility shall permit trading only in security-based swaps that are not readily susceptible to manipulation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Monitoring of trading and trade processing","label":"4 Monitoring of trading and trade processing","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/4/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F4%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/4/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/4/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F4%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"trading procedures to be used in entering and executing orders traded on or through the facilities of the security-based swap execution facility; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/4/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/4/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F4%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"procedures for trade processing of security-based swaps on or through the facilities of the security-based swap execution facility; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/4/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F4%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"monitor trading in security-based swaps to prevent manipulation, price distortion, and disruptions of the delivery or cash settlement process through surveillance, compliance, and disciplinary practices and procedures, including methods for conducting real-time monitoring of trading and comprehensive and accurate trade reconstructions.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":"Ability to obtain information","label":"5 Ability to obtain information","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/5/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/5","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F5%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"establish and enforce rules that will allow the facility to obtain any necessary information to perform any of the functions described in this subsection;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/5/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/5","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F5%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"provide the information to the Commission on request; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/5/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/5","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F5%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"have the capacity to carry out such international information-sharing agreements as the Commission may require.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":"Financial integrity of transactions","label":"6 Financial integrity of transactions","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The security-based swap execution facility shall establish and enforce rules and procedures for ensuring the financial integrity of security-based swaps entered on or through the facilities of the security-based swap execution facility, including the clearance and settlement of security-based swaps pursuant to .section 78c–3(a)(1) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"7","heading":"Emergency authority","label":"7 Emergency authority","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/7","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F7","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The security-based swap execution facility shall adopt rules to provide for the exercise of emergency authority, in consultation or cooperation with the Commission, as is necessary and appropriate, including the authority to liquidate or transfer open positions in any security-based swap or to suspend or curtail trading in a security-based swap.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"8","heading":"Timely publication of trading information","label":"8 Timely publication of trading information","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/8","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F8","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/8/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/8","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F8%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The security-based swap execution facility shall make public timely information on price, trading volume, and other trading data on security-based swaps to the extent prescribed by the Commission.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Capacity of security-based swap execution facility","label":"B Capacity of security-based swap execution facility","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/8/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/8","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F8%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The security-based swap execution facility shall be required to have the capacity to electronically capture and transmit and disseminate trade information with respect to transactions executed on or through the facility.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"9","heading":"Recordkeeping and reporting","label":"9 Recordkeeping and reporting","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/9","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F9","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/9/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/9","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F9%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/9/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/9/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F9%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"maintain records of all activities relating to the business of the facility, including a complete audit trail, in a form and manner acceptable to the Commission for a period of 5 years; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/9/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/9/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F9%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"report to the Commission, in a form and manner acceptable to the Commission, such information as the Commission determines to be necessary or appropriate for the Commission to perform the duties of the Commission under this chapter.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Requirements","label":"B Requirements","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/9/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/9","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F9%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Commission shall adopt data collection and reporting requirements for security-based swap execution facilities that are comparable to corresponding requirements for clearing agencies and security-based swap data repositories.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"10","heading":"Antitrust considerations","label":"10 Antitrust considerations","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/10","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F10","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/10/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/10","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F10%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"adopt any rules or taking any actions that result in any unreasonable restraint of trade; or1So in original. Probably should be “take”.1","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/10/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/10","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F10%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"impose any material anticompetitive burden on trading or clearing.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"11","heading":"Conflicts of interest","label":"11 Conflicts of interest","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/11","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F11","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/11/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/11","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F11%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"establish and enforce rules to minimize conflicts of interest in its decision-making process; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/11/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/11","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F11%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"establish a process for resolving the conflicts of interest.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"12","heading":"Financial resources","label":"12 Financial resources","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/12","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F12","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/12/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/12","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F12%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The security-based swap execution facility shall have adequate financial, operational, and managerial resources to discharge each responsibility of the security-based swap execution facility, as determined by the Commission.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Determination of resource adequacy","label":"B Determination of resource adequacy","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/12/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/12","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F12%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/12/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/12/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F12%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"enables the organization to meet its financial obligations to its members and participants notwithstanding a default by the member or participant creating the largest financial exposure for that organization in extreme but plausible market conditions; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/12/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/12/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F12%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"exceeds the total amount that would enable the security-based swap execution facility to cover the operating costs of the security-based swap execution facility for a 1-year period, as calculated on a rolling basis.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"13","heading":"System safeguards","label":"13 System safeguards","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"are reliable and secure; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"have adequate scalable capacity;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the timely recovery and resumption of operations; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the fulfillment of the responsibilities and obligations of the security-based swap execution facility; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/C/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FC%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"order processing and trade matching;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/C/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FC%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"price reporting;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/C/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FC%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"market surveillance; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iv","heading":null,"label":"iv","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/C/iv","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/13/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F13%2FC%2Fiv","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"maintenance of a comprehensive and accurate audit trail.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"14","heading":"Designation of chief compliance officer","label":"14 Designation of chief compliance officer","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/14","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F14","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/14/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–4/d/14","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78c%E2%80%934%2Fd%2F14%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Each security-based swap execution facility shall designate an individual to serve as a chief compliance officer.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiv